{"type":"message","id":"456c1e8a","parentId":"8fad6eed","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:50:15.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了，看到评论框了！页面结构是：\n- ref=e345: \"说点什么...\" - 这是评论框的 placeholder\n- ref=e347: 评论输入区域\n- ref=e376: \"发送\" 按钮 (disabled) - 发送按钮，现在是禁用的\n\n根据之前的成功经验，流程是：\n1. 点击评论框聚焦 (ref=e345 或 ref=e347)\n2. 设置 innerText 输入评论文字\n3. 触发 input 事件\n4. 点击发送按钮 (ref=e376)\n\n但等等，这个 snapshot 里评论框已经展开了（能看到发送和取消按钮），说明可能已经有人点过了？或者这是默认状态？\n\n不管怎样，我先试试点击评论框，然后输入文字。之前成功的关键是：\n1. 找到 contenteditable 元素\n2. 点击聚焦\n3. 设置 innerText\n4. 触发 input 事件\n\n让我看看 ref=e345 是\"说点什么...\"，这应该是评论框。我先点击它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！看到评论框了（ref=e345 \"说点什么...\"）。按照之前的成功经验，我先点击评论框聚焦：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fea7694bcf094282903b4a53","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","ref":"e345","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e345"},"targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":35266,"output":604,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772178604071}}
