{"type":"message","id":"c589bdfa","parentId":"67f784b8","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:50:22.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，点击成功了，URL 也变成了帖子详情页（/explore/...）。现在需要输入评论文字。\n\n之前成功的关键是用 JS 直接设置 innerText，然后触发 input 事件。让我用 evaluate 来执行 JS 代码。\n\n我需要：\n1. 找到评论框元素（contenteditable）\n2. 设置 innerText\n3. 触发 input 事件\n\n让我用 evaluate 执行 JS：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"成了！现在用 JS 直接输入评论文字（之前成功的关键步骤）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2b6231b12eb4430892b91b6c","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"document.querySelector('[contenteditable]').innerText = '测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍'; const event = new Event('input', { bubbles: true }); document.querySelector('[contenteditable]').dispatchEvent(event);","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":35786,"output":334,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36120,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772178615886}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a18d663","parentId":"c589bdfa","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:50:22.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2b6231b12eb4430892b91b6c","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"browser\",\n  \"error\": \"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: page.evaluate: Error: Invalid evaluate function: Unexpected token ';'\\n    at anonymous (eval at evaluate (:290:30), <anonymous>:19:17)\\n    at UtilityScript.evaluate (<anonymous>:292:16)\\n    at UtilityScript.<anonymous> (<anonymous>:1:44))\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"browser","error":"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: page.evaluate: Error: Invalid evaluate function: Unexpected token ';'\n    at anonymous (eval at evaluate (:290:30), <anonymous>:19:17)\n    at UtilityScript.evaluate (<anonymous>:292:16)\n    at UtilityScript.<anonymous> (<anonymous>:1:44))"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772178622095}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3047d3a","parentId":"6a18d663","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:50:31.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"操，JS 代码里有分号，导致解析失败。我需要把 JS 代码写成一个函数体，而不是多行语句。\n\n让我改成：\n```js\n() => {\n  const el = document.querySelector('[contenteditable]');\n  el.innerText = '测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍';\n  el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true }));\n}\n```\n\n但 fn 参数应该是一个函数字符串... 让我看看之前的用法。\n\n其实更简单的方式是把整个函数体写成一个字符串，不带分号，用逗号或者换行。\n\n或者我可以试试把代码写在一行，用 void 操作符：\n```js\nvoid function(){const el=document.querySelector('[contenteditable]');el.innerText='测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍';el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input',{bubbles:true}))}()\n```\n\n但这样还是有分号问题。让我看看错误信息... \"Invalid evaluate function: Unexpected token ';'\"\n\n可能 fn 参数期望的是一个函数定义，而不是函数调用。让我试试只写函数体：\n```js\nfunction(){const el=document.querySelector('[contenteditable]');el.innerText='测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍';el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input',{bubbles:true}))}\n```\n\n或者更简单，直接返回一个函数：\n```js\n()=>{const el=document.querySelector('[contenteditable]');el.innerText='测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍';el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input',{bubbles:true}))}\n```\n\n但分号还是会有问题... \n\n我意识到 Playwright 的 evaluate 可能需要不同的处理方式。也许可以用更简洁的箭头函数，避免复杂的语句分隔。关键是要找到一个能绕过语法限制的写法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，分号问题。让我把 JS 写成单行箭头函数：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2eadc605d354fd4b1a55f5f","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"()=>{const el=document.querySelector('[contenteditable]');el.innerText='测试评论：这帖子写得不错👍';el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input',{bubbles:true}))}","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":36204,"output":888,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37092,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772178622099}}
