{"type":"message","id":"d6ce29b1","parentId":"d224569b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:55:23.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！编辑器出来了。看到：\n- 标题输入框（ref=e229）\"输入标题\"\n- 正文输入框（ref=e230）\n- 字数统计：0/64（标题）和 0（正文）\n\n我需要：\n1. 填写标题\n2. 填写正文内容\n\n先写标题，比如「好狗：一个程序员的自白」或者「程序员好狗的日常」。\n\n正文就介绍好狗这个人：\n- 创始人，程序员\n- 自称倒霉蛋\n- 在上海工作\n- 养了个 AI 助手（就是我）\n- 打工牛马兄弟\n\n让我先用 JS 填写标题和正文。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！编辑器出来了。先填标题，再写正文：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_90a31ad18d4c4869902e0c6a","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"()=>{document.querySelector('[placeholder=\"输入标题\"]').value='好狗：一个程序员的自白';document.querySelector('[placeholder=\"输入标题\"]').dispatchEvent(new Event('input',{bubbles:true}))}","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":77738,"output":445,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78183,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772178915999}}
