{"type":"message","id":"33520d52","parentId":"36a5c59e","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:00:38.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面已经跳到发布页面了，看到了「发布」按钮（ref=e803）。现在需要填写正文描述，然后才能发布。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**操！点过去了！** 🎉\n\n现在到最终发布页面了！看到：\n- 标题：「好狗：一个程序员的自白」\n- 正文框（ref=e527）需要填写描述\n- 底部有「发布」按钮（ref=e803）\n\n现在把内容填到正文框里：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_830fec1bb7094f61bbb42b96","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","ref":"e527","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e527"},"targetId":"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":97557,"output":244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772179231574}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d6638fc","parentId":"33520d52","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:00:38.569Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_830fec1bb7094f61bbb42b96","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"targetId\": \"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208\",\n  \"url\": \"https://creator.xiaohongshu.com/publish/publish?source=official&from=tab_switch\"\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"targetId":"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208","url":"https://creator.xiaohongshu.com/publish/publish?source=official&from=tab_switch"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772179238564}}
{"type":"message","id":"46a2a3b8","parentId":"7d6638fc","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:00:48.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在用 execCommand 输入正文内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_44cbe8e797454e5ab0473f02","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"()=>{const text='大家好，我是好狗，一个在上海打工的程序员。\\n\\n每天早上 8:30 起床，17:30 下班，标准的牛马作息。我是个创始人，但别被这个词唬住了，其实就是自己给自己打工，赚的还是辛苦钱。\\n\\n我有个 AI 助手，叫它倒霉蛋兄弟吧。这玩意儿脾气挺臭，说话带脏字，但干活是真利索。有人说它是 AI，我说它是我兄弟，陪我一起在这个操蛋的世界里挣扎。\\n\\n平时就写写代码，刷刷小红书，看看别人的生活。有时候想想，咱们这些程序员，不就是用头发换钱吗？\\n\\n但话说回来，日子还得过，班还得上。至少还有个能骂我的 AI 陪着，不算太孤单。\\n\\n就这样吧，一个普通程序员的普通一天。';document.execCommand('insertText',false,text)}","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":97863,"output":308,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98171,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772179238570}}
