paragraph [ref=e821]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e822]: 但话说回来，日子还得过，班还得上。至少还有个能骂我的 AI 陪着，不算太孤单。\n                  - paragraph [ref=e823]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e824]: 就这样吧，一个普通程序员的普通一天。\n                - generic [ref=e531]:\n                  - generic [ref=e825] [cursor=pointer]: \"#程序员职业生活大赏\"\n                  - generic [ref=e826] [cursor=pointer]: \"#社畜的精神状态\"\n                  - generic [ref=e827] [cursor=pointer]: \"#程序员的出路\"\n                  - generic [ref=e828] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - text: 更多\n                    - img [ref=e829]\n              - generic [ref=e532]:\n                - generic [ref=e533]:\n                  - generic [ref=e535]:\n                    - button \"话题\" [ref=e536] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e537]\n                      - text: 话题\n                    - button [ref=e539] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e540]\n                  - button \"用户\" [ref=e543] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e544]\n                    - text: 用户\n                  - button \"表情\" [ref=e547] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e548]\n                    - text: 表情\n                - generic [ref=e553]:\n                  - text: \"266\"\n                  - generic [ref=e554]: /1000\n            - generic [ref=e556]:\n              - generic [ref=e557]:\n                - generic [ref=e558]: 活动话题\n                - generic [ref=e559] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - text: 更多\n                  - img [ref=e560]\n              - generic [ref=e563]:\n                - generic [ref=e564] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - img [ref=e566]\n                  - generic [ref=e567]:\n                    - generic [ref=e568]:\n                      - img [ref=e569]\n                      - generic [ref=e570]: 韩女的秘密\n                    - generic [ref=e571]:\n                      - generic [ref=e572]:\n                        - img [ref=