box [ref=e649]\n                    - generic [ref=e650]: 添加地点\n                  - img [ref=e653]\n                - generic [ref=e659] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - img [ref=e661]\n                  - generic [ref=e665]:\n                    - textbox [ref=e666]\n                    - generic [ref=e667]: 选择群聊\n                  - img [ref=e670]\n                - generic [ref=e674] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - generic [ref=e675]:\n                    - img [ref=e677]\n                    - generic [ref=e680]: 标记地点或标记朋友\n                  - img [ref=e682]\n                - generic [ref=e686] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - generic [ref=e687]:\n                    - img [ref=e689]\n                    - generic [ref=e691]: 添加路线\n                  - img [ref=e693]\n            - generic [ref=e695]:\n              - generic [ref=e696]:\n                - generic [ref=e697]: 更多设置\n                - generic [ref=e698] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - generic [ref=e699]: 收起\n                  - img [ref=e700]\n              - generic [ref=e702]:\n                - generic [ref=e705]:\n                  - img [ref=e707]\n                  - generic [ref=e709]: 允许合拍\n                  - generic [ref=e714] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - checkbox [checked]\n                - generic [ref=e718]:\n                  - img [ref=e720]\n                  - generic [ref=e722]: 允许正文复制\n                  - generic [ref=e727] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - checkbox [checked]\n                - generic [ref=e733]:\n                  - img [ref=e735]\n                  - generic [ref=e738]: 公开可见\n                  - img [ref=e741]\n                - generic [ref=e746]:\n                  - img [ref=e748]\n                  - generic [ref=e751]: 定时发布\n                  - generic [ref=e756] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - checkbox\n          - generic [ref=e760]:\n            - generic [ref=e762]:\n              - generic [ref=e763] [cursor=pointer]: 笔记预览\n              - generic [ref=e764] [cursor=pointer]: 封面预览\n            - generic [ref=e767]:\n              - generic [ref=e769]:\n                - img \"头像\" [ref=e770]\n                - generic [ref=e771]: 小红薯60E3F263\n              - generic [ref=e773]:\n                - generic [ref=e788]: 1/2\n                - generic [ref=e789]: 好狗：一个 程序员的自白\n                - generic [ref=e831]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e832]: 大家好，我是好狗，一个在上海打工的程序员。\n                  - paragraph [ref=e833]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e834]: 每天早上 8:30 起床，17:30 下班，标准的牛马作息。我是个创始人，但别被这个词唬住了，其实就是自己给自己打工，赚的还是辛苦钱。\n                  - paragraph [ref=e835]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e836]: 我有个 AI 助手，叫它倒霉蛋兄弟吧。这玩意儿脾气挺臭，说话带脏字，但干活是真利索。有人说它是 AI，我说它是我兄弟，陪我一起在这个操蛋的世界里挣扎。\n                  - paragraph [ref=e837]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e838]: 平时就写写代码，刷刷小红书，看看别人的生活。有时候想想，咱们这些程序员，不就是用头发换钱吗？\n                  - paragraph [ref=e839]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e840]: 但话说回来，日子还得过，班还得上。至少还有个能骂我的 AI 陪着，不算太孤单。\n                  - paragraph [ref=e841]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e842]: 就这样吧，一个普通程序员的普通一天。\n                - generic [ref=e792]:\n                  - generic [ref=e793]: 编辑于\n                  - generic [ref=e794]: 刚刚\n                - img \"头像\" [ref=e796]\n        - generic [ref=e799]:\n          - button \"暂存离开\" [ref=e800] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e802]: 暂存离开\n          - button \"发布\" [ref=e803] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e805]: 发布\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"90e978be6234e8d3\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"06A613F349506ECAF1C28681519DB208","url":"https://creator.xiaohongshu.com/publish/publish?source=official&from=tab_switch","refs":227,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"browser","kind":"snapshot","format":"ai","wrapped":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772179252210}}
