{"type":"message","id":"6b8192f5","parentId":"edd69af7","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:04:14.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是通知页面，看到瀚森 hansen 啊回复了\"谢谢\"。但这是评论通知，不是私信。\n\n私信应该在别的地方。让我看看页面底部右侧有个 iframe（ref=e977），可能是聊天窗口？或者需要点\"我\"的页面找私信入口。\n\n让我先看看有没有私信相关的标签或按钮。通知页面有 3 个标签：\n- 评论和@（ref=e983）\n- 赞和收藏（ref=e985）\n- 新增关注（ref=e987）\n\n私信不在这。让我点\"我\"的页面看看。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_87b6ca10ba194a5995cfe749","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","ref":"e599","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e599"},"targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":121142,"output":378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772179445682}}
