{"type":"message","id":"3d06d8da","parentId":"0f56d3d5","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:05:22.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"通知页面只有\"评论和@\"、\"赞和收藏\"、\"新增关注\"三个标签，没有私信。\n\n页面右下角有个 iframe（ref=e154），可能是聊天组件。让我看看能不能访问它或者找到私信入口。\n\n用户说\"回复一下嘟啦\"，\"嘟啦\"可能是个用户名。让我试试搜索一下或者找找有没有消息相关的入口。\n\n实际上，小红书 web 端的私信功能可能不在这个通知页面。让我试试访问用户个人主页，看看有没有发消息的按钮。\n\n或者，让我用 JS 找找页面上有没有消息相关的元素。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8b9f5e2c2e28407e9c17be50","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"()=>{const btns=document.querySelectorAll('button,a,div[role=\"button\"]');Array.from(btns).forEach((b,i)=>{if(b.textContent.includes('消息')||b.textContent.includes('私信')||b.textContent.includes('chat')||b.textContent.includes('Message')){console.log(i,b.textContent,b.href||'no href')}})}","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":131842,"output":408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772179508786}}
