{"type":"message","id":"768431b1","parentId":"77c8c006","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:05:28.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没找到消息相关的按钮。让我试试访问 /api/messages 或者其他路径，或者看看 iframe 里有什么内容。\n\n实际上，用户说\"看看私信，回复一下嘟啦\"，可能\"嘟啦\"是之前联系过的人。让我试试直接访问用户主页，或者用搜索功能找\"嘟啦\"。\n\n但首先，让我看看能不能访问小红书的消息页面，可能路径不是/messages。常见的路径还有：\n- /message\n- /chat\n- /dm\n- /inbox\n\n让我试试 /message（单数）。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_170be977379b4e8ab51f1c71","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"95EF6198E12D75042A146862045C9793","targetUrl":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/message"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":132209,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132529,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772179522798}}
